{"tid":1239294,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"5年前已經有人識用聖詩保命","createTime":"2019-06-18T06:22:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T06:27:45.000Z","uid":229607,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"418f8ae7f0fe7d9ccaa9aa7e624136554ed1c2fb","tid":1239294,"uid":229607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:22:48.000Z","msg":"有無人仲記得2014呢單新聞? <br />\n3個鐘已經足已令綁匪放人, 班警犬果日聽左6個鐘, 應該五臟六腑都五勞七傷了... 想保命建議快d 去睇獸醫<br />\n<br />\nWillie被擄了上車，心知不妙，口中就開唱起福音歌《EveryPraise》來。他不斷地唱，不理會綁匪的呼喝，綁匪聽到Willie的歌星極不耐煩，駕車四處轉了三小時後，終於吃不消，把Willie趕了下車。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20140421/52402137?fbclid=IwAR0aKO3OcKTrFJkX4Nu-5OKvoGnNyhZ-yyfbiAQr139fYZZ6M33vr1WhL3A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140421%2F52402137%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0aKO3OcKTrFJkX4Nu-5OKvoGnNyhZ-yyfbiAQr139fYZZ6M33vr1WhL3A&d=b2hjM7c23Ds3Tm%2B3KbcyASZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=b73dbbfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20140421%2F52402137%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0aKO3OcKTrFJkX4Nu-5OKvoGnNyhZ-yyfbiAQr139fYZZ6M33vr1WhL3A&h=9baae077\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20140421/52402137?fbclid=IwAR0aKO3OcKTrFJkX4Nu-5OKvoGnNyhZ-yyfbiAQr139fYZZ6M33vr1WhL3A</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NAKYJWq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNAKYJWq.jpg&h=02d48400&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b64670766b86c60684a827166cc3ce9a062691d0","tid":1239294,"uid":147916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T06:25:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c7a4b6d20b83b6d96f664ab364d5e99da4ebf2","